avin is used to manage Avalon Media System batch ingest packages

Commands:

    avin ls [-a] [-c STR]

        List batches

            -a          include batches that have been ingested
            -c STR      limit to collections whose name contains STR

    avin ingest [-na] COLLECTION [PKGDIR...]

        Ingest one or more batches

            -a          ingest all available batches
            -n          dry run -- print what would be done

            COLLECTION  full name of the collection into which to ingest
            PKGDIR...   one or more batch ingest package directories
